    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? This car is in great shape and absolutely ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I just know you\u2019re going to love how smoothly it handles. It's clean, comfy, and just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
