    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is robust, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS bulletproofing already completed. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from proactive rear subframe reinforcement. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this example offers visceral feedback and exceptional lateral grip. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is superlative, making it an ideal candidate for the purist driver seeking a turn-key performance icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
